description.value: Gleefully attempting to devour any magic it has a grab on, it attempts to counter one random active spell or item as if using @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.9HpwDN4MYQJnW0LG]{Dispel Magic} (+14 to counteract) on any creature it has applied the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed} condition to or object it is holding. When an effect or item is dispelled, the ooze gains 5 temporary hit points.

Trigger Being struck with a magic weapon or an unarmed attack of a creature with an active spell effect

Effect The ooze swirls colorfully, trying to draw magic from the triggering target as if using Chaotic Embrace at the moment of impact.
